{"tid":605791,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"楊冪身穿綠衣服與男密友遊大阪","createTime":"2018-03-26T03:41:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-09T19:15:35.000Z","uid":72009,"like":165,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":95,"replies":[{"pid":"575e42faadd85e7e9830440288d48313cf4b2228","tid":605791,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T03:41:06.000Z","msg":"昨有網友在日本大阪環球影城巧遇中國女星楊幂，她穿著螢光綠帽T打扮休閒，身旁還有主持人張大大，兩人正在排隊，胸前都掛著小小兵爆米花桶，看來玩得投入。<br />\n<br />\n雖然楊冪和張大大、Angelababy常曬合照，「閨蜜情」有目共睹，但楊冪與張大大結伴出國，仍引來網友批評「有時間不回家陪老公陪孩子」，對此，楊冪粉絲護主表示，她這趟是去工作順便放鬆，助理也同行，「她在家跟孩子一起又不會時時刻刻出來說」；「難道一個女人結婚了就不能有自己私人時間？都什麼年代了」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.entertainment.appledaily.com/realtime/20180326/1322161\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Frealtime%2F20180326%2F1322161&d=O3%2By7wO7X%2Bwwy%2FDqU%2FGA04zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=d427d512\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Frealtime%2F20180326%2F1322161&h=864c8c01\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.entertainment.appledaily.com/realtime/20180326/1322161</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180326/640_83376d459ad5fb8cab49502c624f3b74.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180326%2F640_83376d459ad5fb8cab49502c624f3b74.jpg&h=222c2095&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180326/640_aa9d53420eb244ddb17d40e0af3d647b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180326%2F640_aa9d53420eb244ddb17d40e0af3d647b.jpg&h=65b046ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180326/640_4502d4efa3be1592ca685736a6e7ab49.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180326%2F640_4502d4efa3be1592ca685736a6e7ab49.jpg&h=